[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":642},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fvscode\u002F20210512\u002F2779926364\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fvscode\u002F20210512\u002F2779926364\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fvscode\u002F20210512\u002F2779926364\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fvscode\u002F20210512\u002F2779926364\u002F":618,"related:\u002Fvscode\u002F20210512\u002F2779926364\u002F":627},"\u002Fen\u002Fvscode\u002F2021\u002F05\u002F12\u002Fvscode-settings-i-recommend-for-developers\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":599,"date":600,"description":18,"extension":601,"lang":602,"meta":603,"navigation":604,"path":605,"readingMinutes":606,"seo":607,"standalone":608,"stem":609,"tags":610,"tldr":614,"updated":615,"url":616,"__hash__":617},"content\u002FVSCode\u002F身為開發者-我會建議你使用的-VSCode-的實用設定.md","身為開發者，我會建議你使用的 VSCode 的實用設定","2779926364",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":589},"minimark",[11,15,19,22,25,32,43,48,55,58,61,67,70,73,76,110,117,122,132,135,141,144,151,156,163,167,174,179,190,195,198,269,273,284,289,292,299,304,308,311,313,585],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"工欲善必先利其器，身為長期有在 VSCode 的工程師來講，如果可以多了解自己的編輯器設定，其實可以幫助自己在實際開發上的方便性以及除錯，因此這一篇我就紀錄與分享一下有哪些 VSCode 的實用設定吧！",[12,20,21],{"id":21},"顯示空格與定位點",[16,23,24],{},"以往我們在使用預設的 VSCode 的時候，基本上你不太會看到小白點(空格與定位點)，所謂的小白點是什麼呢？也就是以下這張圖的樣子：",[16,26,27],{},[28,29],"img",{"alt":30,"src":31},"小白點","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FVSCode\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-05-12%2009.04.24.png",[16,33,34,35,39,40,42],{},"這個功能在 VSCode 叫做「",[36,37,38],"code",{},"renderControlCharacters","」，因此你可以進入到 VSCode 的設定搜尋「",[36,41,38],{},"」",[16,44,45],{},[28,46],{"alt":38,"src":47},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FVSCode\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-05-12%2009.08.57.png",[16,49,50,51,54],{},"除此之外也會建議將「",[36,52,53],{},"renderWhitespace","」改成 All，這樣子就可以看到空格與定位點符號囉。",[16,56,57],{},"而這個功能在實際開發上非常重要，也因此會建議一定要開啟，這樣子才能夠知道自己目前到底使用的是空格還是定位點哩。",[16,59,60],{},"額外補充，一個小白點代表空格，而箭頭則是定位點，呈現方式如下圖：",[16,62,63],{},[28,64],{"alt":65,"src":66},"LF 與 CRLF 差異","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FVSCode\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-05-12%2010.04.44.png",[12,68,69],{"id":69},"預設行尾字元",[16,71,72],{},"如果你是一名前端工程師，又剛好有在使用 ESLint 的話，那麼這個設定我非常建議你要調整。",[16,74,75],{},"首先通常我們開啟檔案時可能會是 CRLF 換行方式，尤其是 Window 開發者最常見，但是許多規範，如 ESLint 都會建議你改成 LF，因此為了解決這個問題你可以進入到 setting 中加入以下這一個屬性：",[77,78,83],"pre",{"className":79,"code":80,"language":81,"meta":82,"style":82},"language-json shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","\"files.eol\": \"\\n\",\n","json","",[36,84,85],{"__ignoreMap":82},[86,87,90,94,98,101,105,107],"span",{"class":88,"line":89},"line",1,[86,91,93],{"class":92},"sTRMh","\"files.eol\"",[86,95,97],{"class":96},"sMAXC",": ",[86,99,100],{"class":92},"\"",[86,102,104],{"class":103},"sWyjQ","\\n",[86,106,100],{"class":92},[86,108,109],{"class":96},",\n",[16,111,112,113,116],{},"又或者是直接到 setting 中搜尋 ",[36,114,115],{},"eol"," 即可找到該設定：",[16,118,119],{},[28,120],{"alt":115,"src":121},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FVSCode\u002F202105120915.png",[16,123,124,125,127,128,131],{},"這個設定是預設行尾字元，使用 ",[36,126,104],{}," 表示 LF，",[36,129,130],{},"\\r\\n"," 表示 CRLF，而通常會需要調整這個設置是因為 CRLF 格式的縮排會導致開發者在換作業系統時，可能有機率性出現程式碼大跑版，因此通常許多規範都會建議使用 LF，畢竟 CRLF 只有在 Window 上。",[16,133,134],{},"額外補充，你也可以調整 tab 的一些設置，例如你期望 tab 等於多少空格，因此你可以搜尋「tabSize」試著調整看看",[16,136,137],{},[28,138],{"alt":139,"src":140},"editor.tabSize","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FVSCode\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-05-12%2009.35.48.png",[12,142,143],{"id":143},"編輯器字型大小",[16,145,146,147,150],{},"有時候可能覺得預設字型太小，因此也可以透過在設定搜尋「",[36,148,149],{},"terminal.integrated.fontSize","」來調整字型大小",[16,152,153],{},[28,154],{"alt":149,"src":155},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FVSCode\u002F202105120918.png",[16,157,158,159,162],{},"反之若要調整編輯器字型大小則是「",[36,160,161],{},"editor.fontSize","」。",[12,164,166],{"id":165},"emmet","Emmet",[16,168,169,170,173],{},"雖然 Emmet 基本上是預設會開啟的，但是還是會有機會遇到設置跑掉的狀況，所以也可以在設定中搜尋「",[36,171,172],{},"triggerExpansionOnTab","」，只需要確定它是否有打勾為主",[16,175,176],{},[28,177],{"alt":165,"src":178},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FVSCode\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-05-12%2009.23.20.png",[16,180,181,182,185,186,189],{},"另外 VSCode 的 emmet 預設只針對特定檔案格式展開，但是例如 ",[36,183,184],{},".ejs、.vue"," 等可能就無法運作，因此就會建議搜尋「",[36,187,188],{},"includeLanguages","」，然後在底下新增即可",[16,191,192],{},[28,193],{"alt":188,"src":194},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FVSCode\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-05-12%2009.25.54.png",[16,196,197],{},"懶人包：",[77,199,201],{"className":79,"code":200,"language":81,"meta":82,"style":82},"\"emmet.includeLanguages\": {\n  \"javascript\": \"javascriptreact\",\n  \"vue-html\": \"html\",\n  \"plaintext\": \"jade\",\n  \"ejs\": \"html\",\n},\n",[36,202,203,211,225,238,251,263],{"__ignoreMap":82},[86,204,205,208],{"class":88,"line":89},[86,206,207],{"class":92},"\"emmet.includeLanguages\"",[86,209,210],{"class":96},": {\n",[86,212,214,218,220,223],{"class":88,"line":213},2,[86,215,217],{"class":216},"sKpQp","  \"javascript\"",[86,219,97],{"class":96},[86,221,222],{"class":92},"\"javascriptreact\"",[86,224,109],{"class":96},[86,226,228,231,233,236],{"class":88,"line":227},3,[86,229,230],{"class":216},"  \"vue-html\"",[86,232,97],{"class":96},[86,234,235],{"class":92},"\"html\"",[86,237,109],{"class":96},[86,239,241,244,246,249],{"class":88,"line":240},4,[86,242,243],{"class":216},"  \"plaintext\"",[86,245,97],{"class":96},[86,247,248],{"class":92},"\"jade\"",[86,250,109],{"class":96},[86,252,254,257,259,261],{"class":88,"line":253},5,[86,255,256],{"class":216},"  \"ejs\"",[86,258,97],{"class":96},[86,260,235],{"class":92},[86,262,109],{"class":96},[86,264,266],{"class":88,"line":265},6,[86,267,268],{"class":96},"},\n",[12,270,272],{"id":271},"emmet-預設值","Emmet 預設值",[16,274,275,276,279,280,283],{},"當然 VSCode 還有額外一個強大的功能，有時候我們使用 ",[36,277,278],{},"!+tab"," 展開 HTML 樣板時，可能 lang 與 charset 都要調整一次，但是 VSCode 允許你預先設置好，之後展開就會呈現你調整的預設值，首先先在 VSCode 設定搜尋「",[36,281,282],{},"emmet.variables","」，並依照相對應設置即可：",[16,285,286],{},[28,287],{"alt":282,"src":288},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FVSCode\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-05-12%2009.31.33.png",[12,290,291],{"id":291},"滾輪放大視窗字型",[16,293,294,295,298],{},"這個設置也是非常實用的功能，以往我們在放大視窗時，可能要按著特定組合按鍵來放大，這樣子其實滿麻煩的，因此 VSCode 也有提供一個功能是按住 CTRL+滾輪放大 VSCode 視窗，可以在搜尋中搜尋「",[36,296,297],{},"mouseWheelZoom","」，並將它打勾即可：",[16,300,301],{},[28,302],{"alt":297,"src":303},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FVSCode\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-05-12%2009.28.39.png",[12,305,307],{"id":306},"懶人-json-包","懶人 json 包",[16,309,310],{},"下面這邊是我上面介紹的完整懶人包，只需要進入到 settings.json 複製貼上即可，但是這邊要注意，如果你有客製化自己的 settings.json，會建議你先複製出一份再個一個屬性貼進去會比較好。",[16,312,197],{},[77,314,316],{"className":79,"code":315,"language":81,"meta":82,"style":82},"{\n    \u002F\u002F emmet tab 展開\n    \"emmet.triggerExpansionOnTab\": true,\n    \u002F\u002F 不支援的語言中啟用 Emmet\n    \"emmet.includeLanguages\": {\n        \"javascript\": \"javascriptreact\",\n        \"vue-html\": \"html\",\n        \"plaintext\": \"jade\",\n        \"ejs\": \"html\",\n    },\n    \u002F\u002F 開啟顯示空白(格)符號\n    \"editor.renderWhitespace\": \"all\",\n    \"editor.renderControlCharacters\": true,\n    \u002F\u002F 預設 HTML 樣板設置\n    \"emmet.variables\": {\n        \"lang\": \"zh-Hant-TW\",\n        \"charset\": \"UTF-8\",\n    },\n    \u002F\u002F tab 預設空格數量\n    \"editor.tabSize\": 2,\n    \u002F\u002F 預設行尾字元，使用 \\n 表示 LF，\\r\\n 表示 CRLF。\n    \"files.eol\": \"\\n\",\n    \u002F\u002F 編輯器字型大小\n    \"editor.fontSize\": 16,\n    \u002F\u002F 終端機字型大小\n    \"terminal.integrated.fontSize\": 16,\n    \u002F\u002F 滑鼠放大視窗字型(按著 CRTL + 滾輪)\n    \"editor.mouseWheelZoom\": true,\n}\n",[36,317,318,323,329,342,347,354,365,377,389,401,407,413,426,438,444,452,465,478,483,489,502,508,524,530,543,549,561,567,579],{"__ignoreMap":82},[86,319,320],{"class":88,"line":89},[86,321,322],{"class":96},"{\n",[86,324,325],{"class":88,"line":213},[86,326,328],{"class":327},"sQrFR","    \u002F\u002F emmet tab 展開\n",[86,330,331,334,336,340],{"class":88,"line":227},[86,332,333],{"class":216},"    \"emmet.triggerExpansionOnTab\"",[86,335,97],{"class":96},[86,337,339],{"class":338},"sCcAr","true",[86,341,109],{"class":96},[86,343,344],{"class":88,"line":240},[86,345,346],{"class":327},"    \u002F\u002F 不支援的語言中啟用 Emmet\n",[86,348,349,352],{"class":88,"line":253},[86,350,351],{"class":216},"    \"emmet.includeLanguages\"",[86,353,210],{"class":96},[86,355,356,359,361,363],{"class":88,"line":265},[86,357,358],{"class":216},"        \"javascript\"",[86,360,97],{"class":96},[86,362,222],{"class":92},[86,364,109],{"class":96},[86,366,368,371,373,375],{"class":88,"line":367},7,[86,369,370],{"class":216},"        \"vue-html\"",[86,372,97],{"class":96},[86,374,235],{"class":92},[86,376,109],{"class":96},[86,378,380,383,385,387],{"class":88,"line":379},8,[86,381,382],{"class":216},"        \"plaintext\"",[86,384,97],{"class":96},[86,386,248],{"class":92},[86,388,109],{"class":96},[86,390,392,395,397,399],{"class":88,"line":391},9,[86,393,394],{"class":216},"        \"ejs\"",[86,396,97],{"class":96},[86,398,235],{"class":92},[86,400,109],{"class":96},[86,402,404],{"class":88,"line":403},10,[86,405,406],{"class":96},"    },\n",[86,408,410],{"class":88,"line":409},11,[86,411,412],{"class":327},"    \u002F\u002F 開啟顯示空白(格)符號\n",[86,414,416,419,421,424],{"class":88,"line":415},12,[86,417,418],{"class":216},"    \"editor.renderWhitespace\"",[86,420,97],{"class":96},[86,422,423],{"class":92},"\"all\"",[86,425,109],{"class":96},[86,427,429,432,434,436],{"class":88,"line":428},13,[86,430,431],{"class":216},"    \"editor.renderControlCharacters\"",[86,433,97],{"class":96},[86,435,339],{"class":338},[86,437,109],{"class":96},[86,439,441],{"class":88,"line":440},14,[86,442,443],{"class":327},"    \u002F\u002F 預設 HTML 樣板設置\n",[86,445,447,450],{"class":88,"line":446},15,[86,448,449],{"class":216},"    \"emmet.variables\"",[86,451,210],{"class":96},[86,453,455,458,460,463],{"class":88,"line":454},16,[86,456,457],{"class":216},"        \"lang\"",[86,459,97],{"class":96},[86,461,462],{"class":92},"\"zh-Hant-TW\"",[86,464,109],{"class":96},[86,466,468,471,473,476],{"class":88,"line":467},17,[86,469,470],{"class":216},"        \"charset\"",[86,472,97],{"class":96},[86,474,475],{"class":92},"\"UTF-8\"",[86,477,109],{"class":96},[86,479,481],{"class":88,"line":480},18,[86,482,406],{"class":96},[86,484,486],{"class":88,"line":485},19,[86,487,488],{"class":327},"    \u002F\u002F tab 預設空格數量\n",[86,490,492,495,497,500],{"class":88,"line":491},20,[86,493,494],{"class":216},"    \"editor.tabSize\"",[86,496,97],{"class":96},[86,498,499],{"class":338},"2",[86,501,109],{"class":96},[86,503,505],{"class":88,"line":504},21,[86,506,507],{"class":327},"    \u002F\u002F 預設行尾字元，使用 \\n 表示 LF，\\r\\n 表示 CRLF。\n",[86,509,511,514,516,518,520,522],{"class":88,"line":510},22,[86,512,513],{"class":216},"    \"files.eol\"",[86,515,97],{"class":96},[86,517,100],{"class":92},[86,519,104],{"class":103},[86,521,100],{"class":92},[86,523,109],{"class":96},[86,525,527],{"class":88,"line":526},23,[86,528,529],{"class":327},"    \u002F\u002F 編輯器字型大小\n",[86,531,533,536,538,541],{"class":88,"line":532},24,[86,534,535],{"class":216},"    \"editor.fontSize\"",[86,537,97],{"class":96},[86,539,540],{"class":338},"16",[86,542,109],{"class":96},[86,544,546],{"class":88,"line":545},25,[86,547,548],{"class":327},"    \u002F\u002F 終端機字型大小\n",[86,550,552,555,557,559],{"class":88,"line":551},26,[86,553,554],{"class":216},"    \"terminal.integrated.fontSize\"",[86,556,97],{"class":96},[86,558,540],{"class":338},[86,560,109],{"class":96},[86,562,564],{"class":88,"line":563},27,[86,565,566],{"class":327},"    \u002F\u002F 滑鼠放大視窗字型(按著 CRTL + 滾輪)\n",[86,568,570,573,575,577],{"class":88,"line":569},28,[86,571,572],{"class":216},"    \"editor.mouseWheelZoom\"",[86,574,97],{"class":96},[86,576,339],{"class":338},[86,578,109],{"class":96},[86,580,582],{"class":88,"line":581},29,[86,583,584],{"class":96},"}\n",[586,587,588],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sWyjQ, html code.shiki .sWyjQ{--shiki-default:#FF9492}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}html pre.shiki code .sQrFR, html code.shiki .sQrFR{--shiki-default:#BDC4CC}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}",{"title":82,"searchDepth":213,"depth":213,"links":590},[591,592,593,594,595,596,597,598],{"id":14,"depth":213,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":213,"text":21},{"id":69,"depth":213,"text":69},{"id":143,"depth":213,"text":143},{"id":165,"depth":213,"text":166},{"id":271,"depth":213,"text":272},{"id":291,"depth":213,"text":291},{"id":306,"depth":213,"text":307},"VSCode","2021-05-12 09:02:38","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fvscode\u002Fvscode","3",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"VSCode\u002F身為開發者-我會建議你使用的-VSCode-的實用設定",[599,611,612,613],"實用設定","Setting","開發",null,"2023-04-16 20:01:00","\u002Fvscode\u002F20210512\u002F2779926364\u002F","_DzWRMQAFtHp841y83FPwckxIVA_b4YAEadVRdJbnYc",{"newer":619,"older":623},{"url":620,"title":621,"date":622},"\u002Fother\u002F20210516\u002F1782510553\u002F","GitHub Pages build failure","2021-05-16 21:00:47",{"url":624,"title":625,"date":626},"\u002Fgit\u002F20210507\u002F1725042940\u002F","git push 出現 GH007: Your push would publish a private email address.","2021-05-07 11:35:23",[628,633,638],{"url":629,"title":630,"date":631,"readingMinutes":632},"\u002Fvscode\u002F20250424\u002F4258825567\u002F","VSCode 找不到 Git，安裝它或使用 \"git.path\" 設置","2025-04-24 09:52:23","1",{"url":634,"title":635,"date":636,"readingMinutes":637},"\u002Fvscode\u002F20240908\u002F3488366595\u002F","GitHub Copilot 好難用？說不定是你不懂 Copilot 之技巧全攻略不藏私！","2024-09-08 13:06:00","5",{"url":639,"title":640,"date":641,"readingMinutes":632},"\u002Fvscode\u002F20231026\u002F54606935\u002F","VSCode 上 Vue 自訂元件失去高亮","2023-10-26 11:03:07",1784011737150]